{
  "stem": "734.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he struggled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at some point the business failed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he had to give up the business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he went to open a different business not far from the city, in a little-- in a community called [INAUDIBLE], which is something like a half an hour by train from Radom.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was still in public school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was probably, at the time, in sixth grade, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had to commute to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the school out there in the village was not very much up-to-date.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we decided that I'll have to commute and to continue at the same school I went to, which was a public school, except that it had very high standards at that time.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for two years, until I finished seventh grade, I had to commute by train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very interesting time for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, I love trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is probably where I fell in love with trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Wherever I go, whatever country I visit, the first thing I do is take a ride on the train, even till now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nowadays, I still love trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No matter how bad they are, I love to listen to the sirens, the lo-- the locomotive, the whistle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, they are not as-- not the same whistles as they used to be in those days.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the school I went to, we had seven Jewish boys in the class of '38, '40.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mickiewicza, named after a 19th c-- 19th century Polish poet, Adam Mickiewicz, who was quite prominent as a poet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, very much so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was very rampant, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we learned how to live with it, although I-- we used to get our beatings regularly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Still--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
